column10:
My favorite RTS.

Good:
* Minimalistic engaging gameplay;
* Huge variety of units;
* Graphics is still good in 2022.

Bad:
* Dumb AI;
* Hard to master multiplayer at times.

I played on Wargame EE for years, and I enjoyed it a lot;
Well, this game is a whole new level of details and awareness, good work.
Moreover, almost 2000 units is a really impressive amount.
Some criticism though :
- Improve AI on its intelligence (althought it's satisfying enough currently);
- Modify the AI behaviour on sea battles, it's just unfunny to play against something so aggressive;
- The more units you would add to the game (Leclerc 140 mm GIAT ftw), the most pleased we would be.

Thank you for reading.
